headline: Analysts Endorse Fiserv’s (FI) Fundamentals, See Pullback as Opportunity
summary: Fiserv Inc. (NYSE:FI) is one of the best large-cap tech stocks to buy now. On July 24, TD Cowen’s Bryan Bergin reiterated his Buy rating on Fiserv but trimmed the price target to $188 from $233. Bergin’s decision came a day after the company reported its Q2 2025 results.
